room_title: Escape room "20,000 Leagues Under the Sea" by Novel Escape in Austin
room_description:
You're a prisoner on a submarine, and the captain has offered you one chance at escape: find for him the ancient treasure hidden deep at the bottom of the ocean..

The catch? Your air runs out in ONE HOUR.

It's a race against the clock. Do you have what it takes to scour the ocean floor, capture the treasure, and make it back to the surface before you run out of time?
